{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Line a square cake tin (20 cm) with plastic wrap, extending plastic approximately 5 cm over the edges and set aside.","Place 100 g of the pistachios into mixing bowl and mill <b>1 min\/speed 10<b>, until a fine dust consistency is achieved. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Without cleaning mixing bowl, place hazelnuts and figs into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b> . Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place butter, cream, chocolate, golden syrup and brandy (optional) into mixing bowl and cook <b>3 min\/80°C\/speed 2<b>, until smooth.","Add biscuits, remaining 50 g pistachios and reserved hazelnut mixture and combine <b>15 sec\/\/speed 1<b>.","Transfer mixture into prepared tin, press into corners and smooth surface, ensuring that there are no air pockets. Cover with plastic wrap and place into refrigerator for 4 hours or until set.","Remove slice and allow to stand for 10 minutes. Turn slice out onto a chopping board and remove plastic wrap. Dust half with reserved pistachio dust and half with cocoa powder then cut into thin slices or small squares and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["150 g pistachio nuts","120 g hazelnuts, without skin, roasted","5 dried figs, cut into halves","50 g butter, cut into pieces","50 g pouring (whipping) cream","300 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces","2 tbsp golden syrup","2 tbsp brandy              (optional)","100 g digestive biscuits broken into pieces (approx. 3 cm)","cocoa powder, for dusting"]}],"id":"r108365","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-0Wrwbc-m1Kc\/XZWciNHCaNI\/AAAAAAAAebA\/mivCkf1vg_EUDb-aDySbMiUTSOFAmQUjQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_0yjEXU2nruQESspT.png","title":"Tiffin slice","publishedAt":"2016-03-20T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3.41 g","fat":"14.27 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13.32 g","calories":"835 kJ \/ 198 kcal"},"usefulItems":"square cake tin (20 cm), plastic wrap, bowl, wooden chopping board, refrigerator","basicInfo":["easy","15m","4h 30m","25 portions"]}